  m_text: I went through one of the doors, i dont know which direction, but it opened
    to another room, and as I stepped into the room, the doors locked behind me.
    There was a thing in there with a gaunt face that shot something at me.. and
    almost in response, i dont know how i did it but i was able to shoot a burst
    of energy at it multiple times and it exploded
